HEADWORD: Breakneck
<hw>Break"neck`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
fall that breaks the neck.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A steep place endangering the neck.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Breakneck</ent>⟦br⟧

